    dc:description "Figs. 11-17. Tyloperla khang. 11. Head and pronotum. 12. Male terminalia. 13. Hemitergal process, dorsal. 14. Hemitergal process, lateral. 15. Aedeagus, lateral. 16. Female terminalia. 17. Vagina and spermateca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758923/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758565>
    dc:description "Figs. 18-20. Tyloperla khang egg structures. 18. Entire egg, lateral. 19. Egg collar end with anchor. 20. Opercular ring and lid." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758565/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4758559>
    dc:description "Figs. 1-6. Tyloperla courtneyi. 1. Head and pronotum. 2. Male terminalia. 3. Hemitergal process, dorsolateral. 4. Aedeagus, lateral. 5. Female terminalia. 6. Vagina and spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4758559/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

